metadata.name: Two Souls I
metadata.description:
Two Souls - a part of our still abstract series of 1/1 artworks brought into life by using different shades of 2 colors with a oil paint touch to it visible up close.

It represents two different souls finally coming together. 
The artwork has different meaning for everyone and that's the beauty of it. For some it may represent domination, to some love, it can be a mix of emotions or the feeling of surrender at the same time.
